--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The minivorbis decoder (minivorbis.c) is a modified version of Sean Barrett's
stb_vorbis. It, like the original, is public domain.
(Enabled with -DALIB_OGG_SUPPORT) OGG support is enabled by default.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Portions of the Xiph.org Speex codec source code (libspeex) are contained in the
'speex' folder and compiled by default. They fall under a BSD-like license.

